{"tid":194582,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尋晚去男朋友屋企食飯,臨走伯母叫我拎返走個生果,咩意思?","createTime":"2017-04-10T05:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T15:12:05.000Z","uid":76059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d0cecedecf303ecbfbcd7f8d10cf63f167f9f86a","tid":194582,"uid":76059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T05:24:24.000Z","msg":"尋晚去男朋友屋企食飯<br />\n兩手空空上去唔係咁好<br />\n就係UNY買左份生果上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁食飯都有講有笑<br />\n食完飯就食個生果<br />\n<br />\n食完唔夠5分鐘話夜叫我走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n臨走時伯母叫我拎返我買上黎淨底個生果返屋企食,咩意思?  (當然最後無拎)<br />\n<br />\n男朋友話係客氣先咁對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以我所知送野俾人又俾番人地係無禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n是咪唔應該再上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:非hehe"},{"pid":"b4e678272bb68d82d501e5fb5cd9109695a64bb2","tid":194582,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T05:27:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d0874b5473da652fe358a7aec12afa92665e92f","tid":194582,"uid":94508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T05:28:26.000Z","msg":"叫得你走無望啦<br />\n係當你自己人咁夜仲唔留你過夜扑野等抱孫咩"},{"pid":"2a8b8fbd8048d30e5a949fbbbfd83bf8e9e2d123","tid":194582,"uid":76059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T05:29:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫得你走無望啦<br />\n係當你自己人咁夜仲唔留你過夜扑野等抱孫咩</blockquote><br />\n問題唔係我自己中上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係佢地叫我黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99fe1886b81b6a95faeb02208ad27c509b3dfdcf","tid":194582,"uid":76059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T05:30:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫你食蕉啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係買蕉<img src=\"/assets